69. Sessions Courts shall have no jurisdiction in actions, suits or
proceedings of a civil nature—
(a) relating to immovable property except as provided in
sections 70 and 71;
(b) (Deleted by Act A1382);
(c) (Deleted by Act A1382);
(d) (Deleted by Act A1382);
(e) to enforce trusts;
